    "The second module is the anonymizer, which takes the places associated with those entities and removes or replaces them.",
    "INCOGNITUS implements the analyzer module combined with a pretrained Spacy language model (Montani et al., 2020) and leverages the anonymizer module to produce anonymized text content.",
